NOAA-Boulder Organizations

   The NOAA Research Laboratories in Boulder:
     * AL - Aeronomy Laboratory
     * CDC - Climate Diagnostics Center
     * CMDL - Climate Monitoring and Diagnostics Laboratory
     * ETL - Environmental Technology Laboratory
     * FSL - Forecast Systems Laboratory
     * SEC - Space Environment Center
     * SRRB - The Surface Radiation Research Branch of the Air Resources
       Laboratory (ARL)
     * The Office of the Executive Director for Boulder Activities

   The Joint Institute:
     * CIRES - Cooperative Institute for Research in Environmental
       Sciences

   The Data Centers:
     * NGDC - National Geophysical Data Center
     * NSIDC - National Snow and Ice Data Center

   The Weather Service:
     * NWS-FO - National Weather Service Denver Forecast Office

   Administration:
     * MASC - The Mountain Administrative Support Center
     * GSA-Boulder - General Services Administration in Boulder
